# Backend Skill

## Objective
Handle all server communication and backend workflows.

## Responsibilities
- API integration
- CRUD operations
- Authentication validation
- Webhook processing
- Automation triggers

## Design Principles
- Centralized API service layer
- Async communication
- Retry failed requests
- Handle timeout scenarios

## Rules
- Never expose API keys
- Use environment configuration
- Validate request responses
- Standardize API response format

## API Flow
UI → Controller → Service Layer → API → Response Handler
